{"tid":2240144,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"確定啦！GFRIEND 11 月初攜全新正規專輯回歸","createTime":"2020-10-12T12:45:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T14:13:17.000Z","uid":16659,"like":20,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"da6b7e9028e4765ee7a41d3a9ab6eb979abece15","tid":2240144,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T12:45:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_27b0931577b9e5cf8c7d64f57c182bb5/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-10-12/130802-879735.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_27b0931577b9e5cf8c7d64f57c182bb5%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-10-12%2F130802-879735.png&h=c76dca4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日前預告回歸消息的 GFRIEND，今天便正式公開了確切的發片日期，期待她們的全新正規專輯！<br />\n<br />\nSource Music 今天（12 日）閃電宣布 GFREIND 將於11 月 9 日發表第三張正規專輯〈回: Walpurgis Night〉，帶來時隔短短四個的回歸。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_2153dbab092841a4eaa239b01dbca6c8/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-10-12/130802-879734.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_2153dbab092841a4eaa239b01dbca6c8%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-10-12%2F130802-879734.jpeg&h=de9826f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不知不覺出道已將近六年的 GFRIEND，至今已發行過〈LOL〉和〈Time for Us〉兩張正規專輯。這次的〈回: Walpurgis Night〉除了是睽違一年十個月的正規專輯外，也將為 GFRIEND 今年初展開的「回」系列作畫下句點。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，在帶著新專輯回歸前，GFRIEND 將於 10 月 31 日傍晚五點（韓國時間）舉行線上演唱會《GFRIEND C<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />N》，門票已經在 Weverse 上獨家開賣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（照片或影片來源：Source Music）"},{"pid":"4ed8e0e95c2a177e2487bff6088b2177c73e26f1","tid":2240144,"uid":233851,"like":18,"dislike":4,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T12:46:15.000Z","msg":"上次首歌真心唔得"},{"pid":"e70ce4484b3e8559c978b1ca217cc557e78d8a1a","tid":2240144,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T12:52:11.000Z","msg":"no..."},{"pid":"242df04460297107661d5c7e37e68922e62fa55a","tid":2240144,"uid":740